 in police officers an attitude of arrogance, aggressiveness and the general idea that “they” are now not only the “cou</span><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">rt of law” themselves but are indeed completely above the law.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">If you don’t change this, then there is no point in having a police force at all.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">December 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>